 - 
                                         
 
Granted Veridex, LLC, a Johnson & Johnson company, access to GeneChip technology to create and market in vitro diagnostics for cancer through the "Powered by Affymetrix" program
 - 
                                         
 
Translational Medicine
 
Continued to drive translation of basic research discoveries into clinical utility through translational medicine relationships
 - 
                                         
 
Partnered with IBM to deliver tools to accelerate translational and information-based medicine
 - 
                                         
 
