- Shipping and handling costs billed to customers for product shipments are recorded in "net sales" and the related cost is included in "cost of sales" in the Consolidated Statements of Operations. Revenues from shipping and handling costs totaled $281,171 and $233,497 for the nine months ended September 30, 2008 and 2007, respectively.
 
Advertising costs are expensed as incurred.  Advertising expenses were $117,447 and $80,627 for the nine months ended September 30, 2008 and 2007, respectively.
