.   As of the date of your signature below, you agree that you have received all compensation and benefits owed to you by the Company (except, if you sign and do not revoke this Agreement, the Separation Benefits).  As of the date of your signature below, you have no employment-related claims against the Company and have no intention of filing such claims in the future.  You further acknowledge that you have not assigned any claims arising out of your employment to any third party.
