Pursuant to the Amended and Restated Agreement and Plan of Merger (the "Merger Agreement") dated as of May 3, 2012, by and among the Company, Excalibur Acquisition Sub, Inc., a Delaware corporation and wholly owned subsidiary of the Company ("Excalibur"), eBioscience Holding Company, Inc., a Delaware corporation ("eBioscience"), subject to the conditions set forth therein, subsequent to the Closing Date, Excalibur is to be merged with and into eBioscience (the "Merger"), with eBioscience surviving as a wholly-owned subsidiary of the Company.
