(b) If by 11:00 a.m. New York City time, on the Fundamental Change Repurchase Date the Trustee (or other paying agent appointed by the Issuer) holds money sufficient to make payment on all the Notes or portions thereof that are to be repurchased on such Fundamental Change Repurchase Date then:
(i) such Notes shall cease to be Outstanding,
