Item 5.07    Submission of Matters to a Vote of Security Holders
The annual meeting of the stockholders (the "Meeting") of Affymetrix, Inc. ("Affymetrix") was held on May 7, 2013. 60,433,940 shares of Affymetrix common stock were present at the Meeting, representing 85.04% of a total of 71,064,260 shares of common stock outstanding and eligible to vote at such time.
 
 
Consequently, all nominees were elected to the Board of Directors by the stockholders of Affymetrix.
 
 
 
 
 
Board of Directors Leadership
On May 7, 2013, the independent Directors of Affymetrix elected Jami Dover Nachtsheim as the Company's lead director.
